There's also an empty array left behind in node JSON (e.g. when copying):
```json
{
    "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
            "boolean": [],
            "string": [],
            "dateTime": []
        }
    },
    "name": "IF",
    "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if"
}
```

